    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A game of Spanish origin, played on a three -walled or enclosed court, in which two, four or six players catch and return the ball using either their bare hands or a basket-like rackets fastened to the hand.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
